1409
01:17:19,733 --> 01:17:25,067
SWEETHEART, YOU DESERVE IT.

1410
01:17:29,933 --> 01:17:33,266
THANK YOU, MEMAW.

1411
01:17:33,267 --> 01:17:34,432
MERRY CHRISTMAS.

1412
01:17:34,433 --> 01:17:36,400
OHH.

1413
01:17:48,300 --> 01:17:52,732
