ANGER, AFTER I'D BEEN...

1415
01:17:55,500 --> 01:17:57,833
OH, HALLE. WE KNOW.

1416
01:18:04,100 --> 01:18:06,132
I HAD WRITER'S BLOCK,

1417
01:18:06,133 --> 01:18:10,199
