INSPIRED ME TO WRITE

1418
01:18:10,200 --> 01:18:13,899
WHAT MY BOOK IS REALLY
GONNA BE ABOUT.

1419
01:18:13,900 --> 01:18:17,200
I'M NOT JUST A PAWN WHO GETS
MOVED FROM HOME TO HOME ANYMORE.

1420
01:18:21,533 --> 01:18:24,833
SO, WHAT FINALLY GOT YOU GOING?

1421
01:18:27,367 --> 01:18:31,733
ALL OF YOU HAVE TOUCHED MY
HEART IN DIFFERENT WAYS.

1422
01:18:35,600 --> 01:18:37,832
I FEEL SO CONNECTED
TO ALL OF YOU

1423
01:18:37,833 --> 01:18:40,100
IN A WAY I'VE NEVER FELT BEFORE.

1424
01:18:42,400 --> 01:18:44,767
I'M NEW TO THE WHOLE
