1425
01:18:47,333 --> 01:18:50,899
WHEN YOU HAVE ONE, YOU HOLD ON.

1426
01:18:50,900 --> 01:18:52,099
RIGHT, MEMAW?

1427
01:18:52,100 --> 01:18:53,900
OH, THAT'S RIGHT, BABY.

1428
01:18:56,400 --> 01:18:58,932
