1433
01:19:15,900 --> 01:19:17,099
YES, MA'AM.

1434
01:19:17,100 --> 01:19:18,500
AND I'LL GET DREW.

1435
01:19:21,333 --> 01:19:23,599
UM, HALLE, CAN I HAVE A MOMENT?

1436
01:19:23,600 --> 01:19:24,733
SURE.

1437
01:19:27,400 --> 01:19:32,566
THE GIFTS THAT YOU GAVE US,
