1438
01:19:32,567 --> 01:19:34,466
I FIGURED YOU'D NEED
BUSINESS CARDS

1439
01:19:34,467 --> 01:19:38,166
FOR YOUR BOOK SIGNINGS
AND WHATEVER.

1440
01:19:38,167 --> 01:19:41,832
WELL...

1441
01:19:41,833 --> 01:19:45,899
I WANTED YOU TO HAVE THIS.

1442
01:19:45,900 --> 01:19:48,932
IT BELONGED TO YOUR FATHER.

1443
01:19:48,933 --> 01:19:51,599
AND SINCE H.D. MADISON
AND HOWARD MOORE

1444
01:19:51,600 --> 01:19:54,266
HAVE THE SAME INITIALS,

1445
01:19:54,267 --> 01:19:59,732
I FIGURED THAT BELONGED TO YOU.

1446
01:19:59,733 --> 01:20:01,832
YOU GOT A FIRST EDITION
OF MY BOOK?

1447
01:20:01,833 --> 01:20:06,132
WELL, I WAS WRITING YOU A NOTE
