1451
01:20:31,933 --> 01:20:34,699
<i>NOW</i> LET'S GO EAT.

1452
01:20:34,700 --> 01:20:36,167
COME ON.

1453
01:20:37,633 --> 01:20:41,332
OKAY, EVERYBODY.
CHRISTMAS BRUNCH IS SERVED.

1454
01:20:41,333 --> 01:20:44,299
MEMAW, ARE Y'ALL
TRYING TO GET ME FAT?

1455
01:20:44,300 --> 01:20:46,299
