1477
01:21:42,700 --> 01:21:45,532
OHH. OHHH.

1478
01:21:45,533 --> 01:21:49,067
AND I DROVE DOWN ALL
THE MUDDIEST ROADS I COULD FIND.

1479
01:21:50,333 --> 01:21:52,366
